  "texts": [
    "To achieve a meaningful clinical comparison of efficacy and safety in a datadriven way, our framework relies on the definition of a 'baseline' experiment against which to compare results.",
    "The baseline experiment must use the same input data points as the new experiment.",
    "To clearly attribute an experiment's results to a specific change, we aim only to alter one parameter from the baseline experiment configuration at a time.",
    "We used different methodologies to assess and improve model output as described below:",
    "Model Improvements: This outlines modifications to individual LLM calls within our workflow while preserving the same overall structure."
  ]
